  "title": "유학생 상담 프로그램 안내",
  "category": "비교과프로그램",
  "published_at": "2026-03-13",
  "detail_url": "https://www.dongguk.edu/article/INTSTUNOTICE/detail/26763949",
  "content_text": "동국대학교 글로벌학생팀에서는 유학생 여러분의 정서적 안정과 한국 생활 적응을 지원하기 위해 유학생 상담 프로그램을 운영합니다. 유학생 여러분의 많은 신청과 참여 부탁드립니다.\n1. 대상\n동국대학교에 재학 중인 외국인 유학생\n2. 상담 일정\n2026.03.18.(수) ~ 06.09.(화) 기간 중 매주 수요일 12:00 ~ 16:00\n(1회 상담 약 50분)\n3. 상담 장소\n혜화관 617호 글로벌라운지 내 글로벌상담센터\n4. 상담 언어\n한국어 / 영어\n5. 상담 내용\n학업, 대인관계, 진로, 한국 생활 적응 등과 관련한 고민\n6. 신청 방법\n신청 링크 :\nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header\n※ 상담 내용은 비밀이 보장됩니다.\n※ 상담 일정은 신청 상황에 따라 조정될 수 있습니다.\n[English Version]\nInternational Student Counseling Program\nThe Office of International Students at Dongguk University offers an International Student Counseling Program to support the emotional well-being of international students and help them adjust to life in Korea. We encourage all international students to apply and participate actively.\n1. Eligibility\nInternational students currently enrolled at Dongguk University\n2. Counseling Schedule\nEvery Wednesday, 12:00 – 16:00\nDuring the period: March 18, 2026 – June 9, 2026\n(Each session lasts approximately 50 minutes)\n3. Location\nGlobal Counseling Center, Room 617, Global Lounge, Hyehwa Hall\n4. Languages Available\nKorean / English\n5. Counseling Topics\nAcademic matters, interpersonal relationships, career planning, and adjustment to life in Korea\n6. How to Apply\nApplication link:\nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header\n※ All counseling sessions are confidential.\n※ Counseling schedules may be adjusted depending on availability.\n[中文版]\n留学生心理咨询项目 안내\n东国大学全球学生团队为支持留学生的心理健康及韩国生活适应，提供 留学生心理咨询项目。欢迎所有留学生 踊跃报名和参与。\n1. 对象\n东国大学在读外国留学生\n2. 咨询时间\n2026年3月18日 ～ 6月9日期间，每周三 12:00 – 16:00\n（每次咨询约50分钟）\n3. 咨询地点\n惠化馆 617号 Global Lounge 内 Global Counseling Center\n4. 咨询语言\n韩语 / 英语\n5. 咨询内容\n学业、人际关系、职业规划及韩国生活适应等相关问题\n6. 申请方式\n申请链接：\nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header\n※ 咨询内容将严格保密。\n※ 咨询时间可能根据预约情况进行调整。",
  "content_html": "<p>\n\n</p><p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">동국대학교 글로벌학생팀에서는 유학생 여러분의 정서적 안정과 한국 생활 적응을 지원하기 위해 유학생 상담 프로그램을 운영합니다. 유학생 여러분의 많은 신청과 참여 부탁드립니다.</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">1. 대상</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">동국대학교에 재학 중인 외국인 유학생</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">2. 상담 일정</span></span></p>\n<p><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>2026.03.18.(수) ~ 06.09.(화) 기간 중 매주 수요일 12:00 ~ 16:00</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>(1회 상담 약 50분)</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">3. 상담 장소</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">혜화관 617호 글로벌라운지 내 글로벌상담센터</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">4. 상담 언어</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">한국어 / 영어</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">5. 상담 내용</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">학업, 대인관계, 진로, 한국 생활 적응 등과 관련한 고민</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">6. 신청 방법</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>신청 링크 : <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"><span style=\"background-color:#FFFF00;\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header</span></span></a></strong></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">※ 상담 내용은 비밀이 보장됩니다.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">※ 상담 일정은 신청 상황에 따라 조정될 수 있습니다.</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">[English Version]</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">International Student Counseling Program</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">The Office of International Students at Dongguk University offers an International Student Counseling Program to support the emotional well-being of international students and help them adjust to life in Korea. We encourage all international students to apply and participate actively.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">1. Eligibility</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">International students currently enrolled at Dongguk University</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">2. Counseling Schedule</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>Every Wednesday, 12:00 – 16:00</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>During the period: March 18, 2026 – June 9, 2026</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>(Each session lasts approximately 50 minutes)</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">3. Location</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">Global Counseling Center, Room 617, Global Lounge, Hyehwa Hall</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">4. Languages Available</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">Korean / English</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">5. Counseling Topics</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">Academic matters, interpersonal relationships, career planning, and adjustment to life in Korea</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">6. How to Apply</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>Application link: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"><span style=\"background-color:#FFFF00;\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNrDxNuBeLZBLs-rvoKfNd-Gb7lzDtghPTzmcYn8QGMZ5EPg/viewform?usp=header</span></span></a></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">※ All counseling sessions are confidential.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">※ Counseling schedules may be adjusted depending on availability.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">[中文版]</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">留学生心理咨询项目 안내</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">东国大学全球学生团队为支持留学生的心理健康及韩国生活适应，提供 留学生心理咨询项目。欢迎所有留学生 踊跃报名和参与。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">1. 对象</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">东国大学在读外国留学生</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">2. 咨询时间</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>2026年3月18日 ～ 6月9日期间，每周三 12:00 – 16:00</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><u><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong>（每次咨询约50分钟）</strong></span></span></u></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">3. 咨询地点</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">惠化馆 617号 Global Lounge 内 Global Counseling Center</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>